<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.logging.ILogger.CloneLogger" Title="CloneLogger method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.ILogger">ILogger</PageRef> ->
    CloneLogger
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>CloneLogger</TypeRef> method creates a new logger object with the same scope and logging destination as the current logger.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[ILogger::unique_ptr CloneLogger() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="ILogger!cobalt.logging.ILogger">
        A new <TypeRef>ILogger</TypeRef> object wrapped in <TypeRef>ILogger::unique_ptr</TypeRef>.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
